{"tid":746163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香 港 人 ] 就 算 失 望，不 能 絕 望","createTime":"2018-07-17T10:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T10:05:46.000Z","uid":127929,"like":46,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d70c7fb84e83f044e1872888688eb60640386583","tid":746163,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"今日呢個政府做埋咁多缺德既野<br />\n<br />\n佢地一步一步咁影響我地既地方<br />\n<br />\n的確令我地香港人好傷心同失望<br />\n<br />\n但係我地絕對唔可以放棄，因為<br />\n<br />\n基本上呢幾年係政府話得事既人<br />\n<br />\n官員，選舉主任，政務官，等等<br />\n佢地總有一日要退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港倒數<span style=\"color: red;\">最後29年</span>，我地新一代<br />\n<br />\n要用<span style=\"color: red;\">利用剩餘既時間</span>，忍辱負重<br />\n<br />\n爬上管理階層，<span style=\"color: red;\">做話得事個堆人</span><br />\n<br />\n勿忘初心，<span style=\"color: red;\">救返香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">btw,新一代指90後only,用慣大陸野既00後收檔啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d6435b5e33b9058a46f7b5a83c5e1fae85439edf","tid":746163,"uid":53196,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"咁快分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27b90541bfb12a290ca7baf14ae66083a03ebfb","tid":746163,"uid":64884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n但我哋其中要做嘅嘢係令00後加入我哋陣營令佢哋知道中共幾可恥<br />\n如果唔係再過多20年只會他朝君體也相同"},{"pid":"530e852a44fa9f9231d2a31af90261f3fda4e763","tid":746163,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"出一個李登輝唔係易事<br />\n做到蔣經國已經好叻<br />\n更多嘅係變咗汪精衞<br />\n<br />\n講咗咩<br />\n自己參透<br />\n唔明嘅人唔會做到以上任何一個"},{"pid":"fd5d1ca3149981dcfcff54636f4a2277b3e55765","tid":746163,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"太過幼稚 <br />\n到時掌權嘅中高層九成九係大陸出世嘅腥港人啦"},{"pid":"8d260e1009a7fea5e698ae727138ab0cbc1d9e44","tid":746163,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6435b5e33b9058a46f7b5a83c5e1fae85439edf","tid":746163,"uid":53196,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"咁快分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"最重要既係29年時間唔多，80後潛哂水，00 後唔爭氣累事無撚用，<br />\n<br />\n得返90 後開始大個進入社會幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e2e47de1d8af21479ac34002cef6a0eccafaad","tid":746163,"uid":111253,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"受港英教育大嘅 6/7/80後都奶共奶到咁，仲想旨意90後？更唔好講班樂於接受赤化嘅00後，信我，到時到你上位必然奶共，利益大於一切"},{"pid":"4c85da6f727e9968653c1a6fa8ae43770be2a1aa","tid":746163,"uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a523af81437740701bf32352d5d196e4290d71d","tid":746163,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd5d1ca3149981dcfcff54636f4a2277b3e55765","tid":746163,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"太過幼稚 <br />\n到時掌權嘅中高層九成九係大陸出世嘅腥港人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"00後最早個批基本上唔會有足夠時間上到權力高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bbf6b0adeb6c31b0c00f7cff5f9769f368e39d","tid